**Registry system:**
- get_feature_extractor(domain) - factory function
- register_feature_extractor(domain, factory) - custom registration
- list_available_domains() - discovery

Available domains: code, docstring, text, generic

**Docstring-specific features:**
- DocstringClarityFeature: Sentence complexity (10-15 words =3D optimal)
- DocstringCompletenessFeature: Structural elements (Args, Returns, Examples)
- DocstringKeywordDensityFeature: Technical keyword usage (5-15% =3D optimal)

